1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v3 7.5
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity 
Vendor: Siemens 
Equipment: Industrial Products 
Vulnerabilities: Use After Free, Deadlock, Allocation of Resources Without Limits or Throttling 

2. RISK EVALUATION
